<SECOND>BC-APN--Coyotes, Adv 20,1156</SECOND>
<NOTE>$adv20
^AGENCIES AND RADIO OUT</NOTE>
<NOTE>For Release Sunday, March 20</NOTE>
<HEAD>From AP Newsfeatures</HEAD>
<NOTE>(APN SUNDAY ILLUSTRATIONS: Mailed print subscribers get 2 b&amp;w
