TION> Moody </ORGANIZATION>'s Investment Grade Corporate Bond Index, which measures price movements on 80 corporate bonds with maturities of five years or longer, was off 0.64 to 283.78 Yields on three-month <ORGANIZATION> Treasury </ORGANIZATION> bills rose 2 basis points to 5.72 percent. A basis point is one-hundredth of a percentage point. Six-month bills were unchanged at 5.95 percent and one-year bills rose 3 basis points to 6.30 percent. The federal funds rate, the interest on overnight loans between banks, traded at 6 | percent, up from 6 -LCB- percent late Friday
